content_text: My daily routine is a bit upside down because I start my day at around 12 in the noon because we've been working for UK shift. Anas as you might be aware that the UK ship you keep people are five hours and 30 minutes behind the India time. That is the reason I start my day a little late. So once I start I I get up, I go through my normal daily routine like you know, taking a bath, getting ready for the office. Once I go to office the first thing I do is I start reading my emails and I get to know what are the things are lying to me for that given day and I start working on those topics and you know I keep on working till till I don't get enough time to take a break.
